      "id": "PopularPost262707",
      "post_content": "The ability of Jade Monolith is unique enough that it deserves to be a rare. It combos nicely with the Circles of Protection. While the initial casting cost is a bit steep, the activation cost is more than reasonable for what it does. Use this in an aggressive deck to save your high power / low toughness creatures from chump block deaths, or to kill of multiple blockers while keeping your fatty alive. ",
      "posted_by": "Eppek_the_Goblin",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost262707\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_post\">The ability of Jade Monolith is unique enough that it deserves to be a rare.  It combos nicely with the Circles of Protection.  While the initial casting cost is a bit steep, the activation cost is more than reasonable for what it does.  Use this in an aggressive deck to save your high power / low toughness creatures from chump block deaths, or to kill of multiple blockers while keeping your fatty alive. </span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '262707'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy525\">Eppek_the_Goblin</span>\r\n                                (8/15/2012 6:48:29 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src